{"tid":1055112,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸又嚟咗香港","createTime":"2019-03-10T10:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T11:38:02.000Z","uid":196445,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3043c488b065287166a2d4807cc2af0102a41703","tid":1055112,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"萬人迷碧咸不時來港出席活動，原來他偶爾也喜歡來港小休數天，昨日碧咸在Instagram的story上載到中環四季酒店日本食肆跟師傅及職員合照，至今日下午就往銅鑼灣濕平。<br />\n<br />\n今日下午5時許，碧咸在數名保鑣陪同下抵達銅鑼灣百德新街Fashion Walk一間服裝店，引來過百途人圍觀。《蘋果》記者見碧咸一入店內即試鞋及試衫，雖然門外有過百人圍觀及舉手機拍照，但碧咸表現大方任影唔嬲，見他雙手放在身後四圍巡視揀衫，甚至當眾脫下黑色上衣，只穿白色底衫試衫，其間有fans跟他揮手，碧咸都有報以微笑和揮手，表現極為親民。短短15分鐘，碧咸已火速掃了4對鞋及數件外套，據知，碧咸是次花了3萬多元購物。<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟佢都幾鍾意香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23c6eed9f6931a0d6d1b61ff97ae233bd7d1492","tid":1055112,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679d9a7c5fac7c83228123804321fac3dac612cf","tid":1055112,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"有錢真係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尻買都買到三皮幾野"},{"pid":"4d12d0d748200f3a4eb8436747c1f6f3fab2071e","tid":1055112,"uid":146435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"679d9a7c5fac7c83228123804321fac3dac612cf","tid":1055112,"uid":141871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"有錢真係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尻買都買到三皮幾野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:09:00.000Z","msg":"你話係女人街買3皮野就話難姐 係名店買一件分分都成萬啦"},{"pid":"c8263face5692f6519ef2aed2f5b4ff211c9ba77","tid":1055112,"uid":61416,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"679d9a7c5fac7c83228123804321fac3dac612cf","tid":1